<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
	<title>Leave Request</title>
</head>
<body>
<% if @incharge.name.present? %>
Dear <%= @incharge.name%>,
<% else %>
Dear Sir,
<% end %>
<br><br>
<%= @employee.name %> has applied for leave from <%= @leave.start_date.strftime("%d-%m-%Y") %> to <%= @leave.end_date.strftime("%d-%m-%Y") %> for the reason: <%= @leave.reason %>
</br>
Login to your account at <a href="http://www.manaple.com">Manaple</a> to Approve/Reject this request.
</br>

Regards,<br>
Team Manaple
</body>